
**APPLICATION ARCHITECTURE**

LegalVault/
├── backend/
│   ├── admin/            # Admin configurations
│   ├── alembic/          # Database migrations
│   │   ├── versions/     # Migration version files
│   │   ├── env.py       # Alembic environment configuration
│   │   └── alembic.ini  # Alembic configuration file
